{"tid":1333583,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【721新手裝備攻略】無論和理非同勇武都要帶定物資去行去野餐！！！","createTime":"2019-07-19T18:20:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T20:47:49.000Z","uid":146454,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"bf14c9b41403fdc1ab33e0888b90d94614460798","tid":1333583,"uid":146454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T18:20:57.000Z","msg":"相信大家都好熱愛香港，星期日會去港島和平遊行。<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但係過去幾次遊行，都發生左嚴重警民衝突。</span><br />\n<br />\n為左減低前線不必要受傷機會，<span style=\"color: orange;\">無論你支唔支持激進行動，都應該出一分力，帶少少物資，減少物質站嘅壓力之餘， 亦都可以幫下前線同路人。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: navy;\">個個都可以帶嘅物資</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 水(除咗自用亦都可以留一兩支畀物資站)<br />\n2. <strong>口罩，退熱貼</strong><br />\n3. 保鮮紙+膠紙(可以遮鞋 防胡椒噴霧) <br />\n4. <strong>津路或者其他烏龍茶(如果中椒，清理效果勁過生理鹽水)</strong><br />\n5. <strong>長遮</strong>，特別係IKEA<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">尖</span></strong>遮<br />\n6. <strong>手套</strong>(盡量唔好用普通嘅勞工手套， 要買3m嘅防割手套)<br />\n7. <strong>報紙(百搭嘅用品，能攻能守</strong>，<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><del><span style=\"color: purple;\">實驗證明施永青將會係我哋最堅定嘅支持者，佢揸旗嘅免費報紙最厚攻擊力最強，可以打到人腦震盪。</span> 大家識做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></del></span>)</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">如果你係和理非，但係你又想幫多啲手，你可以帶:</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 食材，例如雞蛋，蕃茄，薯子同牛奶。</span></span></strong><br />\n冇殺傷力之餘， 亦都可以對犬隻，藍絲同鬼有羞辱之效。<br />\n可以ff下我地嘅對手一路黐住一大pat蛋汁同臭奶同我地對峙會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>普通嘅衫，T-shirt，最好素色</strong></span>，天時暑熱要換衫㗎嘛<br />\n3.<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> <strong>頭盔</strong>(記得要配埋<strong>V字帶</strong></span>，如果唔係會戴得好辛苦)+<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>3M眼罩or泳鏡/防霧雪鏡</strong></span>(前者容易攞，而後兩者貴少少但係效果比普通鏡高好多)<br />\n4. <strong>泳池用嘅水槍，浮板，波子棋</strong>，暑假梗係要玩多啲㗎喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n5. <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>藥物(例如喉糖，胃藥，醋，哮喘藥，同埋止痛藥)</strong></span><br />\n6. <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>大聲公</strong></span>(文具店，深水埗站旁福榮福華街大把)<br />\n7. <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>勞作品(粗索帶，魔術點，蠟筆)</strong></span><br />\n8. <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">冇用嘅旅行喼</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n如果你想睇下仲可以帶啲咩或者詳細分析，睇埋呢兩個網頁啦:<br />\n1. 【遊戲更新：終極裝備攻略】我在香城Online 2.0 等你～～<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1322657/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1322657/page/1</a><br />\n2. 【7.21】小妹想請所有人去之前一定要入嚟睇下<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1321579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1321579/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n最後提下大家:<br />\n1. 物資通常會喺日本城同埋五金舖有得買，特別係近太子新填地街同埋廣東道一帶嘅舖頭比較多選擇。<strong>亦都因此最近嗰一邊會有好多犬隻。大家小心。</strong><br />\n2. 遊行去到尾聲/撤退嗰陣，<strong>如果冇發生衝突嘅話，盡量幫下物資站清物資啦，攞走一啲相對上 易攞嘅物品，然之後下次攞返黎用</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">上面列出咗大部分前線後方都需要又帶到嘅物資，希望每人都可以帶少少去物資站，咁樣相信前線同後方嘅同路人，都會非常之多謝你哋！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b3V5TAT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb3V5TAT.png&h=dd22a25b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>為自由搏盡，星期日見！<br />\n香港人加油！！</strong><br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"e1e7a561ce48b9c54299d762a120711c03ea6dad","tid":1333583,"uid":146454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T18:21:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">721，讓愛與和平，雞蛋，牛奶和蕃茄佔領軍器廠街</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20fe296c556420668b703f1819786536a148eb3d","tid":1333583,"uid":271833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T18:22:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66147fc19e5b99f900341d8712eba4a5f5b8b65b","tid":1333583,"uid":271833,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T18:22:58.000Z","msg":"一齊頂住，一個都不能少呀<br />\n知道嗎"},{"pid":"df6711ea1ec0ac93725d47b74b5952eae0b17895","tid":1333583,"uid":146454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T18:23:50.000Z","msg":"721：民陣一係唔好搞集會遊行，一搞就要係百萬級嘅人數<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1333107/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1333107/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n[721置頂] 警犬部署分析<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1333423/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1333423/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n等我為大家回憶下決定721去定唔去<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1324531\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1324531</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n無論你選擇做咩角色，企喺咩位置，都請你721出嚟！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1324446\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1324446</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n721嘅和理非入嚟，你地係保護勇武嘅最後一道防線<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1322165\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1322165</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n【 突發】助攻美國戰線《香港人權與民主法案》！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1322642\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1322642</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n【7.21】小妹想請所有人去之前一定要入嚟睇下<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1321579\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1321579</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n【置頂：終極裝備攻略】我在香城Online等你！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1321785\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1321785</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n【遊戲更新：終極裝備攻略】我在香城Online 2.0 等你～～<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1322657\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1322657</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n【721置頂重推】金鐘天眼地圖<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1324427\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1324427</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n律師有野講<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1323465\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1323465</a>"},{"pid":"8d935d98162ae4bac28e34fe28b9f86db81542aa","tid":1333583,"uid":146454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T18:24:33.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">push 推上熱門<br />\n721 見</span></strong>"},{"pid":"85c0a4bf83b03e669783a4a7be9a30759ea89354","tid":1333583,"uid":146454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T18:24:44.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">push 推上熱門<br />\n721 見</span></strong>"},{"pid":"6fafb58d8826d912f057706ce2329d5b63f02a7c","tid":1333583,"uid":146454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T18:24:57.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">push 推上熱門<br />\n721 見</span></strong>"},{"pid":"6663a6eca2aa0a2c9bc0eba06466e6605b67b792","tid":1333583,"uid":146454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T18:25:25.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">push 推上熱門<br />\n721 見</span></strong>"},{"pid":"4f94f5cffbe56890a6ab0265a666ec366cbcce97","tid":1333583,"uid":271833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T18:25:56.000Z","msg":"721見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7be8746266e95587b385dac6fe61d0b17b3dedea","tid":1333583,"uid":233325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T18:26:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c592fcc082e9cb3aef6e69e4647bd8dbce029292","tid":1333583,"uid":146454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T18:26:58.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">721熱門post去曬邊度?</span></strong>"},{"pid":"77337951f